      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "The babies kick us off. ANDER'S DREAM (5) wasn't disgraced in a much richer contest last time out and will appreciate the sharp drop back in company here. Should appreciate the extra trip and is sure to take plenty of stopping. BRUMAL (1) is facing the starter for the first time but has shown ability at the trials and won't need to be a superstar to be competitive against this lot. Keep very safe. SPIRIT OF TORQUE (8) just missed the frame in town on debut and will have derived a stack of benefit from that race day experience. Can feature with natural improvement. ZOU ZOU KAPADOKIA (4) has gotten better with each career run and that culminated with a placing around this circuit at the latest effort. In the mix for some minor money. GLEN'S HEN (6) next best from the favourable draw.",
